= Rabbit

A presentation tool

  * Impl.: Ruby/GTK+ 2/cairo
  * Env.: PC-UNIX/Win/Mac
  * Format: RD/Wiki/PDF
  * View: Ruby(('note:(separated with format)'))

= Features: Display (1)

  * ((*Emphasis*))/(('del:Deletion'))
  * Sub(('sub:script'))/Super(('sup:script'))
  * Math characters: (('&sum;'))(('sub:i=0'))(('&sum;sub:i=0'))
  * Colorized source

= Features: Display (2)

  * Table
  * Interesting theme
  * Image
    * Many supported formats
    * PNG/JPEG/.../PDF/EPS/SVG

= Features: Display (3)

  * Folding long lines
  * Colorized source
  * Big text

