= Op.: Move

: Next page
   Keys mean the next/Left click

   n, f, j, l, Spc, Ret, +, (('&DownArrow;')),
   (('&RightArrow;')), ...

: Previous page
   Keys mean the prev./Center click

   p, b, k, h, BS, Del, -, (('&UpArrow;')),
   (('&LeftArrow;')), ...

= Op.: Advanced move

: Go to title page
   a, 0, <, Home
: Go to n page
   1-9. +Ctrl = +10, +Alt = +20
: Go to last page
   e, $, >, End

